name: UnspecifiedDisorderOfKidneyAndUreter
title: Unspecified Disorder of Kidney and Ureter
description: OP-10 is the measure ID associated with the codes.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains ICD-9 codes associated with other disorders of the kidney and ureter.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have disorders of the kidney and ureter.),(Inclusion Criteria: ICD-9 codes associated with disorders of the kidney and ureter that are unspecified, or diseases that are classified elsewhere are included in this value set.),(Exclusion Criteria: Diseases that are not related to the kidney or ureter, or those captured in systems other than ICD-9, are excluded from the value set.)
